        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-989952114" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-989952114" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="989952114">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lyzw/">1234567</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-12-22</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">15书95。看的是中华书局版。大师就是大师，前面可见史识之远，附录可见史才之深！易中天的很多现点取自于吕先生，但老易毕竟只是搞美学出身的，功底比吕先生还是差很多。17书10。大师说史，很有味道。比如曹操，魏延，翻案翻得好。不需要故作高深，娓娓道来亦足见功力。附录未细读。 </p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="696570114">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-696570114" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-696570114" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="696570114">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/starlv/">古戈</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-06-24</span>
